  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK165">
<l>aḻukkā ṟuṭaiyark katucālu moṉṉār</l>
<l> vaḻukkiyuṅ kēṭīṉ patu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To those who cherish envy that is enough. Though free from enemies that (envy) will bring destruction.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
